    "However, as highlighted by Yang and Kyun (2022) and Ali (2020), further holistic syntheses are needed.",
    "Our study aims to fill this gap with a comprehensive bibliometric analysis of AI in language education, addressing key research topics, trends, authors, documents, and sources.",
    "This aligns with the framework established by van Eck and Waltman (2017).",
    "We aim to illuminate the potential and challenges in AI-assisted L2 teaching and contribute to the development of effective language teaching methodologies.",
    "The research questions guiding the current study are:"
